Type: Package
Package: exvatools
Title: Value Added in Exports with International Input-Output Table
        Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Enrique", "Feas", , "efeas@runbox.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9431-6051"))
Description: Decomposition of value added in exports in an international
    input-output table framework using the methodologies of Borin and
    Mancini (2019)
    <https://openknowledge.worldbank.org/handle/10986/31533>, Miroudot and
    Ye (2021) <doi:10.1080/09535314.2020.1730308>, Wang et al. (2013)
    <https://econpapers.repec.org/paper/nbrnberwo/19677.htm> and Koopman
    et al. (2014) <doi:10.1257/aer.104.2.459>. Includes commands for easy
    data extraction, calculation of complex matrices and other useful
    tools for geographical and sector trade analysis.
